{"comments":"Playhead indicator for Animation Timeline\n\nA vertical line indicating the current frame position in the timeline,\nwith a draggable head for seeking.\n\n## Features\n\n- Vertical line spanning timeline height\n- Draggable head at top\n- Frame/timecode display in head\n- Keyboard nudge support (left/right arrows)\n- Snap to frame boundaries\n\n## Visual Structure\n\n```\n   ┌──────┐  <- Draggable head with frame display\n   │ 0:30 │\n   └──┬───┘\n      │     <- Vertical line\n      │\n      │\n      ▼\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Component.Motion.Timeline.Playhead as Playhead\n\nHH.slot _playhead unit Playhead.component\n  { currentFrame: Frames 100.0\n  , frameRate: fps24\n  , displayMode: TimeRuler.TimecodeMode\n  , height: 400.0\n  , pixelsPerFrame: 10.0\n  , scrollOffset: 0.0\n  }\n  HandlePlayheadOutput\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Playhead component\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"m","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"constraintAnn":[],"constraintArgs":[{"annotation":[],"contents":"m","tag":"TypeVar"}],"constraintClass":[["Effect","Aff","Class"],"MonadAff"],"constraintData":null,"constraintKindArgs":[]},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Halogen","Component"],"Component"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Component","Motion","Timeline","Playhead"],"Query"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Component","Motion","Timeline","Playhead"],"Input"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Component","Motion","Timeline","Playhead"],"Output"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"m","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"ConstrainedType"},"visibility":"TypeVarInvis